envctl-identity-recover - Recover identity from paper backup


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBenvctl identity recover [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Recover your identity using the 24 recovery words from a paper backup.

.PP
You will be prompted to enter the words and set a new passphrase.

.PP
Examples:
  envctl identity recover
  envctl identity recover --words "apple banana cherry ..."
  envctl identity recover --name myname --words "..."


